    <div class="advantages">
        <h2>Advantages of Web3 and Blockchain:</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Decentralization: No central authority controls the network.</li>
            <li>Security: Data is encrypted and stored across multiple nodes, making it highly secure.</li>
            <li>Transparency: All transactions are recorded on a public ledger, ensuring transparency.</li>
            <li>Trustless Transactions: Transactions can be made without the need for intermediaries.</li>
            <li>Immutable Records: Once recorded, data cannot be altered or tampered with.</li>
            <li>Smart Contracts: Self-executing contracts with predefined conditions.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

